            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7070a9a2-00f1-4460-98bd-878457d987f9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
