<p class="">I must express my thanks to the right hon. Gentleman for his courteous references, but I venture most humbly to assure him that occasional outbursts of party politics are by no means confined to only one side of the House.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-95a72c1d-b9f0-41ba-ab7c-1824641ce138" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
