        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-c08bbf26-61bd-496f-aff4-1d669b1657d3">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-c08bbf26-61bd-496f-aff4-1d669b1657d3">
                Mr. Sparks
