    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-76427ac1-754a-4842-9523-157ff830b5a1">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-76427ac1-754a-4842-9523-157ff830b5a1">
                Mr. Macpherson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-76427ac1-754a-4842-9523-157ff830b5a1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-11-17/debates/bc207a2e-f855-4e9f-b9a7-5b9b8b4c831a/TransportBill#contribution-76427ac1-754a-4842-9523-157ff830b5a1">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I hope that the hon. and learned Gentleman will forgive me. <span id="1470" class="column-number" data-column-number="1470"></span> I have been most liberal in giving way so often.<p></p> It seems to me that we must dispose of these major fallacies with which we have been presented. The right hon. Gentleman the Member for East Stirling made the point about utilisation. In fact, the utilisation figures within the groups are high, as I have no doubt he has found out, because they are able to pass over to a central pool of transport all transport surplus to immediate needs. Those vehicles remain in the central pool. Therefore, the over-all figures would be different from the figures which the right hon. Gentleman quoted for one group.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-76427ac1-754a-4842-9523-157ff830b5a1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-11-17/debates/bc207a2e-f855-4e9f-b9a7-5b9b8b4c831a/TransportBill#contribution-76427ac1-754a-4842-9523-157ff830b5a1">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





